<h2>Elder Law and Medicaid Planning</h2>

<p>As families age, long-term care planning becomes increasingly important. We help Murrysville families protect their assets through Medicaid planning, guardianship proceedings when necessary, and coordination between elder law strategies and existing estate plans. With nursing home costs in Western Pennsylvania exceeding $12,000 per month, planning ahead — ideally at least five years before care is needed — can save families tens of thousands of dollars while ensuring access to quality care.</p>

